description:
ExtremeBtc Token radically improves the efficiency of digital markets and social platforms by creating the EBTC Token that can be exchange between Digital and Social platforms and Users.
ExtremeBtc is a Ethereum based Token and transactions can be tracked on the Ethereum Blockchain.
​
ExtremeBtc was created to connect users and all over the world on a Digital and Social platform with one another creating the EBTC family.
​
EBTC will not only be used as a communication Token but will become a currency incorporated by Merchants world wide as means of payment.
name: ExtremeBTC
